data.description: ASSUMABLE 2.75 % MORTGAGE!!! Welcome home to this spacious 4 bedroom, 3 full bathroom, Bi-level home offering an abundance of living space and a serene and private backyard in the amenity filled community, Emerald Lakes. Upon entering, you are welcomed by a two- story split level Foyer entrance. The main level features a huge and welcoming living room that seamlessly transitions into an open-concept kitchen and dining area. The open design fosters a sense of togetherness, ideal for both everyday living and entertaining. The kitchen boasts an island with seating, perfect for meal preparation or a quick snack. Down the hall there is the master bedroom complete with an en-suite bathroom featuring a jetted tub, a separate shower stall, and dual sink vanity, providing both luxury and functionality. Additionally, another large bedroom, a walk-in closet with shelves allowing for organized storage of clothing and personal items, and full bath equipped with a shower and tub. The lower level is showcased with an expansive family room and rec area, and spacious third and fourth bedrooms. Lastly, there is a laundry room and full bathroom. A two-car oversized garage provides ample space for parking and storage. Outdoor features include a large deck overlooking the private yard, a patio area perfect for relaxation, a whole-house generator for added security & a leaf filter guard system. Enjoy community clubhouse, indoor/ outdoor pools, lake, playground and more! Short Term Rental friendly!
